main event: A UFO report from August 9, 1967, details photographs of a forested area in Dallas, Texas, with some images containing unidentified objects in the sky.
interesting points: The report contains a total of 6 photographs,The photographs show dense forested areas with no visible human subjects,One photograph depicts a partially obscured aerial object hovering above the wooded area,Another photo shows an unidentified object in the sky, obscured by trees,The report is categorized under 'UNCLASSIFIED' by the FOREIGN TECHNOLOGY DIVISION, AFSC.
